WITH RankedMovies AS (
    SELECT 
        a.id AS movie_id,
        a.title AS movie_title,
        a.production_year,
        COUNT(DISTINCT ci.person_id) AS cast_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT an.name, ', ') AS cast_names
    FROM 
        aka_title a
    JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON a.id = ci.movie_id
    JOIN 
        aka_name an ON ci.person_id = an.person_id
    WHERE 
        a.production_year >= 2000
    GROUP BY 
        a.id, a.title, a.production_year
),
MoviesWithKeywords AS (
    SELECT 
        rm.movie_id,
        rm.movie_title,
        rm.production_year,
        rm.cast_count,
        rm.cast_names,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT k.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
    FROM 
        RankedMovies rm
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON rm.movie_id = mk.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
    GROUP BY 
        rm.movie_id, rm.movie_title, rm.production_year, rm.cast_count, rm.cast_names
),
MoviesWithCompany AS (
    SELECT 
        mwk.movie_id,
        mwk.movie_title,
        mwk.production_year,
        mwk.cast_count,
        mwk.cast_names,
        mwk.keywords,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT cn.name, ', ') AS companies
    FROM 
        MoviesWithKeywords mwk
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_companies mc ON mwk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        company_name cn ON mc.company_id = cn.id
    GROUP BY 
        mwk.movie_id, mwk.movie_title, mwk.production_year, mwk.cast_count, mwk.cast_names, mwk.keywords
)
SELECT 
    mwc.movie_id,
    mwc.movie_title,
    mwc.production_year,
    mwc.cast_count,
    mwc.cast_names,
    mwc.keywords,
    mwc.companies
FROM 
    MoviesWithCompany mwc
ORDER BY 
    mwc.production_year DESC,
    mwc.cast_count DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."MOVIE_ID", "t5"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t5"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."CAST_COUNT", "t5"."CAST_NAMES", "t5"."KEYWORDS", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_name"."name", ', ') AS "COMPANIES"
FROM (SELECT "t3"."MOVIE_ID", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t3"."CAST_COUNT", "t3"."CAST_NAMES", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT MIN("s1"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", MIN("s1"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "s1"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(DISTINCT "cast_info"."person_id") AS "CAST_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "CAST_NAMES"
FROM "s1"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "s1"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
WHERE "s1"."production_year" >= 2000
GROUP BY "s1"."id", "s1"."title", "s1"."production_year") AS "t3"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "t3"."MOVIE_ID" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "keyword" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
GROUP BY "t3"."MOVIE_ID", "t3"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t3"."CAST_COUNT", "t3"."CAST_NAMES") AS "t5"
LEFT JOIN "movie_companies" ON "t5"."MOVIE_ID" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
LEFT JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
GROUP BY "t5"."MOVIE_ID", "t5"."MOVIE_TITLE", "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t5"."CAST_COUNT", "t5"."CAST_NAMES", "t5"."KEYWORDS"
ORDER BY "t5"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t5"."CAST_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST
